<p>MySql query:</p>  <pre><code>select 'customers'  tableName , customers.* from customers </code></pre>  <p>This is the serialization function:     </p>  <pre><code>        List&lt;?&gt; received = exchange.getIn().getBody(List.class);         FileOutputStream fich   = new FileOutputStream("xmlop.xml");             XMLEncoder x = new XMLEncoder(new BufferedOutputStream(fich));             x.writeObject(received);             x.flush();             x.close(); </code></pre>  <p>The result</p>  <pre><code>&lt;?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?&gt; &lt;java version="1.8.0_45" class="java.beans.XMLDecoder"&gt;  &lt;object class="java.util.ArrayList"&gt;   &lt;void method="add"&gt;    &lt;object class="org.springframework.util.LinkedCaseInsensitiveMap"&gt;     &lt;void method="put"&gt;      &lt;string&gt;tableName&lt;/string&gt;      &lt;string&gt;customers&lt;/string&gt;     &lt;/void&gt;     &lt;void method="put"&gt;      &lt;string&gt;id&lt;/string&gt;      &lt;int&gt;1&lt;/int&gt;     &lt;/void&gt;     &lt;void method="put"&gt;      &lt;string&gt;firstname&lt;/string&gt;      &lt;string&gt;zied&lt;/string&gt;     &lt;/void&gt;     &lt;void method="put"&gt;      &lt;string&gt;lastname&lt;/string&gt;      &lt;string&gt;saffar&lt;/string&gt;     &lt;/void&gt;    &lt;/object&gt;   &lt;/void&gt;   &lt;void method="add"&gt;    &lt;object class="org.springframework.util.LinkedCaseInsensitiveMap"&gt;     &lt;void method="put"&gt;      &lt;string&gt;tableName&lt;/string&gt;      &lt;string&gt;customers&lt;/string&gt;     &lt;/void&gt;     &lt;void method="put"&gt;      &lt;string&gt;id&lt;/string&gt;      &lt;int&gt;2&lt;/int&gt;     &lt;/void&gt;     &lt;void method="put"&gt;      &lt;string&gt;firstname&lt;/string&gt;      &lt;string&gt;mohamed&lt;/string&gt;     &lt;/void&gt;     &lt;void method="put"&gt;      &lt;string&gt;lastname&lt;/string&gt;      &lt;string&gt;houidi&lt;/string&gt;     &lt;/void&gt;    &lt;/object&gt;   &lt;/void&gt;  &lt;/object&gt; &lt;/java&gt; </code></pre>  <p>What shall i do to have something like this :</p>  <pre><code>&lt;customer&gt;     &lt;id&gt;1&lt;/id&gt;     &lt;firstname&gt;zied&lt;/firstname&gt;     &lt;lastname&gt;saffar&lt;/lastname&gt; &lt;/customer&gt; &lt;customer&gt;     &lt;id&gt;1&lt;/id&gt;     &lt;firstname&gt;zied&lt;/firstname&gt;     &lt;lastname&gt;saffar&lt;/lastname&gt; &lt;/customer&gt; </code></pre>  <p>=> name field as a tag &lt;==</p>